Detailed Description

cvmx_l2c_oob2

L2C_OOB2 = L2C Out of Bounds Range Checker

Description: Defines DMA "Out of Bounds" region #2. If a DMA initiated write transaction generates an address within the specified region, the write is 'ignored' and an interrupt is generated to alert software.
